{
  "stem": "3804.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who are the people?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The other-- other-- other people, not on the 5th Avenue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] in the-- how-- in-- in the small places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I walk a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All-- all my life, I walk all over the world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whenever I've been in the night, I just come out about a few hours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wanted to see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't mind danger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No danger, I do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's why I was mugged three times here in New York.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I still like New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and you-- you were running around the streets of Haifa as a child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Haifa, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What-- what-- what did I do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we have a-- first thing, all my life, I like movies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the first thing, we didn't have money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we have to climb when they-- you know, it was open movies, you know, with no roof.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was really then, I don't know how we stayed alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we-- we ran on a-- you know, on old buildings to see the movie, with no-- not paying money.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I lost my head.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I lost this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I lost that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I-- that's one of things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The second thing is, you know, like every child, stealing small things, you know, chocolate and all this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one-- I tell-- did I tell in my book the accident with the chocolate?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This woman, OK, so we have big sticks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that also helped us, you know, in-- to have some kind of inventions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How to do this and that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's why I was so good later in the secret service because I had a lot of experience of the street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had the atmosphere of the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Big stick with a nail, I took-- put in the chocolate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day, I was caught by a woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
